    "text": "Skip to content\nUK PRESIDENCY\nGLASGOW CLIMATE PACT\nUK AT COP27\nTHE CONFERENCE\nNEWS\nDELIVERING THE\nGLASGOW CLIMATE PACT\n#GLASGOWCLIMATEPACT\n\nUNITING THE WORLD\nTO TACKLE\nCLIMATE CHANGE.\nThe UK hosted the 26th UN Climate Change Conference of the Parties (COP26) in Glasgow on 31 October – 13 November 2021.\nThe COP26 summit brought parties together to accelerate action towards the goals of the Paris Agreement and the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change.\nLearn about how the negotiations at COP26 went and the outcomes achieved in the documents below.\nREAD THE COP26 GLASGOW CLIMATE PACT READ THE COP26 PRESIDENCY OUTCOMES\nCOP26December 7, 2022 1600384616375799808\n\"We just want the chance to live\"\n\nClimate activist @NasaloSalote spoke to us at #COP27 about how sea level rise caused by #ClimateChange is affecting the South Pacific.\n\nWatch the full interview\nTwitter 1600384616375799808\nCOP26December 5, 2022 1599659840384606209\nThe UK Youth Parliament provides opportunities for 11-18 year olds to use their elected voice to change the world for the better.\n\nThe UK #Climate Negotiators will meet with members of the youth parliament this Thursday to discuss the outcomes of #COP27.\n\nLearn more\nTwitter 1599659840384606209\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nThe progress on loss and damage is historic.\n< ...\n294 10\nAs we near the end of #COP27, take a look back thr ...\n757 5\n“We don’t have time.”\n\nClimate activist @A ...\n369 6\nPRIVACY\nCOOKIE POLICY\nTERMS & CONDITIONS\nACCESSIBILITY\nCONTACT\n  TELL US WHETHER YOU ACCEPT COOKIES\nWe use cookies to collect information about how you use UKCOP26.ORG. We use this information to make the website work as well as possible and improve government services.\nACCEPT ALL COOKIES SET COOKIE PREFERENCES",
